@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

### MOVIES: Listar todas
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?page=1&size=10

### MOVIES: Crear una (Exitoso)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Inception",
    "year": 2010
}

### MOVIES: Error 400 (Datos inválidos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "",
    "year": "error"
}

### ACTORS: Obtener uno por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/actors/1

### USERS: Actualizar usuario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jeremie Madera",
    "email": "jmadera@universidad.edu"
}

### ACTORS-MOVIES: Borrar relación
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/actors-movies/15